annotationA: Probable ribosome biogenesis protein RLP24; Involved in the biogenesis of the 60S ribosomal subunit. Ensures the docking of NOG1 to pre-60S particles (By similarity)
annotationB: Ribosomal protein L10Aa; Structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: phagocytosis; translation; neurogenesis
